[normal]A focus on energy efficiency is therefore vital to reduce emissions from industrial heat. The key 
[normal]efficiency 
[normal]technolog
[normal]y that is underexploited in UK industry remains combined heat and power
[normal],
[normal] which delivers a reductio
[normal]n in fuel use of up to 30%
[normal]. 
[normal]C
[normal]ombined heat and
[normal] power (CHP)
[normal] is sourced from gas, biomass, biogas and energy from waste.
[normal] [bold]As an energy 
[normal]efficiency technology, CHP rec
[normal]onciles major issues including
[normal]:
