[normal]However, t[bold]he [bold]Government has not yet committed a dedicate[bold]d budget [bold]for [bold]its [bold]bespoke CHP policy[bold]. This lack of financial commitment [bold]must[bold] be addressed[bold] to ensure investor confidence is created[bold].[bold]E[bold]xisting [bold]gas [bold]CHP[bold] [bold]capacity[bold] [bold]faces challenges[bold]The 
