[normal]o action 
[normal]was taken 
[normal]to return this value to existing CHP operators
[normal]. 
[normal]The impact of this decision, which was implemented in April 2013, is now starting to hit British industry and undermine the competitiveness of 
[normal]CHP
[normal] sites
