[normal]Damaged investor confidence limits new[bold] CHP[bold] investment[bold]M
[normal]uch of the expected investment for new CHP installations will likely come from those companies which operate existing CHP. 
[normal]The CHPA is
[normal] aware of a number of companies who 
[normal]are hesitant 
[normal]to invest in CHP again because of the Government’s 
[normal]decision 
[normal]to remove 
[normal]LEC
[normal]s. For example, 
[normal]E.ON
[normal] has stated that
[normal] the removal of LECs has not given “much encouragement to take further investment”
